body:
It seems like Bronze Ranked is just swarmed with trolls, or people who rage and end up trolling as a result. I find that I win when my team doesn&#039;t have a troll, and lose when we do. The last few days it has been about 50/50 chance of getting landed with one. Sometimes I&#039;ll just mute and keep playing, but when they don&#039;t get a response they seem to then troll through stealing CS, feeding or trying to tell the other team that someone else is trolling.  

The question is;

What is the best way to act when you find there&#039;s a troll on your team? Try talk them out of it? Mute and keep playing?
